query: SELECT cs.sectionNumber, COUNT(cq.id) as question_count FROM complianceSections cs LEFT JOIN complianceQuestions cq ON cs.id = cq.sectionId WHERE cs.sectionType = 'service_user' GROUP BY cs.id, cs.sectionNumber ORDER BY question_count ASC, cs.sectionNumber
